snippet: Palestinians fired at an Israeli military jeep, hitting the vehicle but causing no injuries, and three Palestinian protesters were wounded by Israeli fire, the Israeli military said.
abstract: Palestinians fire at Israeli military jeep along Gaza border, hitting vehicle but causing no injuries, and three Palestinian protesters are wounded by Israeli fire during disturbances along border fence.
lead_paragraph: Palestinians fired at an Israeli military jeep, hitting the vehicle but causing no injuries, and three Palestinian protesters were wounded by Israeli fire, the Israeli military said.

headline.main: Gaza: Gunfire Erupts Along Border With Israel
